    {
      "id": "3364750c-f3ba-8047-979f-d94a2266cede",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors introduce an LLM-based Recommender for Literature - LRS4TP. The goal of the paper is to formulate research topics and questions to help them in their Papers. It DOES NOT WRITE automatically… instead it acts as supervisor. A test on a Bachelor of Arts program suggests promising results - high quality feedback while freeing time from the professors and teaching staff.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "3364750c-f3ba-8047-979f-d94a2266cede",
